          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Preparation of Pu-237 from Np-237 irradiated with",
                "deuterons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "S.Baba",
                "K.Hata",
                "M.Izumo",
                "R.Motoki",
                "T.Sekine"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "2JPNJAE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "2JPNJAE"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".Using the JAERI tandem accelerator",
                "one of the targets was bombarded with 18 MeV deuteron",
                "and the other with 25 MeV deuterons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,ARI,36,564,1985",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,ARI,36,564,1985",
                    "doi": "10.1016/0020-708X(85)90111-5",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "ARI",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "36",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "564"
                      },
                      "date": 1985
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "STTA",
                "BCINT",
                "EDEG",
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two targets were used, each made from stacked foils",
                "containing neptunium layers and aluminum foils to",
                "degrade the energy of the deuterons.",
                "About 30 days later both neptunium targets and",
                "aluminum foils (which contained plutonium recoils)",
                "were dissolved in nitric acid.",
                "Finally, a neptunium target was bombarded to obtain",
                "the cross section s for (d,p) and (d,p+2n) reaction",
                "at 21 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/By authors/.the yields of Pu-236 and Pu-238 were",
                "measured by alpha spectrometry and from the knowledge",
                "of the yield of plutonium."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The anion exchange method mentioned earlier was used",
                "to separate the plutonium from neptunium, aluminum",
                "and from fission products, and the purified plutonium",
                "was evaporated onto a stainless steel disc when its",
                "alpha spectrum was measured with a surface barrier",
                "detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
